'''Leroy Gopal''' (yavutse 6 Nyakanga 1979), ni umukinnyi wa filimi ukomoka muri [[Zimbabwe]]  na afurika [[Afurika y’Epfo|y'Epfo]] , akina komedii kandi ni umuhanzi ijwi .   Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''Yellow Card'' and ''Strike Back''.<ref>https://savannanews.com/leroy-gopal-ayiteyi-asumadu-biography-age-wife-net-worth/</ref>  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 6 Nyakanga 1979 i [[Harare]], muri [[Zimbabwe]].  Igihe Gopal yari afite imyaka 14, se yarapfuye. Afite mukuru we, Claudia Gopal Muvuti wahoze ari nyiricyubahiro [[Zimbabwe]].<ref>https://thenation.co.za/bio/leroy-gopal-biography/</ref> . Yarangije amashuri abanza mu ishuri ribanza rya Blackiston hanyuma ayiga ayisumbuye mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Gateway na Prince Edward Senior School<ref>https://nehandaradio.com/2018/04/28/leroy-gopal-lands-big-role/</ref>.  Afite impamyabumenyi ya BA (Icyubahiro) muri Live Performance na Motion Picture kuva AFDA, Ishuri ryubukungu bwo guhanga <ref>https://sw.autograndad.com/132559/1/leroy-gopal.html</ref>.  Ni umwe mu banyeshuri babiri batsindiye igihembo cyiza cya M-NET Umunyeshuri Wumwaka 2003 na 2004 bikurikiranye<ref>https://savannanews.com/leroy-gopal-ayiteyi-asumadu-biography-age-wife-net-worth/</ref>.  Gopal yashakanye n'umukobwa wo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]], Keletso Molefe kuva 2017.  Abashakanye bafite abana batatu: Kiki Leroy Gopal, Didi Tadiwa, na Mimi Naima<ref>https://wikisouthafrica.co.za/leroy-gopal/</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2000, yerekanye sinema ye ya mbere hamwe na firime ''Yellow Card'' aho yakinnye cyane nkumukinnyi wumupira wamaguru 'Tiyane Tsumba'. Kuva mu 2006 kugeza 2007, yakinnye 'Thabang Ngema' mu ikinamico ya  SABC 3  ''One Way'' yamenyekanye cyane.  Muri 2012, yagaragaye muri sitcom ya SABC 1 '', Ses'Top La'' muburyo bwa 'Oleshe<ref>https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=4465</ref>'<ref>https://3-mob.com/entertainment/leroy-gopal-stars-in-new-medical-drama-debuting-on-sabc-2-on-thursday/</ref>. Muri 2013, yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu gukina urwenya muri [[Afurika]] yepfo wa Filime kuri uru ruhare<ref>https://www.pindula.co.zw/Leroy_Gopal</ref>.  Hamwe nitsinzi kandi agaragara nkumukinnyi wabishoboye, yahawe akazi ko gukina ''serivise za Mzansi Rukundo: Kasi Style'' muri 2013<ref>https://zalebs.com/relationships/leroy-gopal/leroy-gopal-got-married-weekend</ref>. Uruhare rwe ni [[Kenya|umugabo wo muri Kenya]] witwa 'Joshua Pembe'.  Yakinnye kandi muri make ''Binyuze mu Guhaguruka kw'ibaba'' ryerekanwe no mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes .<ref>https://legends.co.za/model/5472/</ref> 

Muri uwo mwaka, yakinnye muri filime ''Seal Team 8'' nk'umunyagitugu wa Tongo 'Tonga'. Hanyuma yagaragaye kuri ''serivise ya Mzansi Magic'' hamwe na 'Abomama' yaje kuba umuntu uzwi cyane murukurikirane<ref>https://briefly.co.za/68043-leroy-gopal-bio-age-wife-parents-movies-tv-shows-awards-profile-net-worth.html</ref>.  Muri 2014, yakinnye muri politiki ya SABC1 ''Ihawu le Sizwe'' . Nyuma yaje gushinga 'Creation Station Entertainment Company'. Leroy yayoboye kandi amashusho yindirimbo Zimbabwe kumuririmbyi Audius Mtawarira <ref>https://groovemagazineinternational.wordpress.com/2014/07/07/know-yourprofile-leroy-gopal/</ref>. 

